  <td>Tiles
  <td>A tile is a essentially an element of the tile stack. It is a square on a given x and y coordinate (iow, in a given tile stack) with a given height and slope.
  <td>Tile* - This is a pointer to a single tile (cannot be converted to a TileRef)
  <td>TileRef - This is essentially the location of a single tile. It stores the (x,y) and height information of a tile (can be easily converted to a Tile*)
